 collecting large scale first hand datasets publications the 5 most recent are displayed more publications early commitment on financial aid and college decision making of poor students evidence from randomized evaluation in rural china chengfang liu linxiu zhang renfu luo scott rozelle brian sharbono jennifer adams yaojiang shi ai yue hongbin li xiaobing wang thomas glauben economics of education review 2011 pdf+ mother's education and child health is there a nurturing effect hongbin li yuyu chen chinese university of hong kong department of economics 2006 pdf+ why does spousal education matter for earnings assortative mating or cross productivity chong huang hongbin li pak wai liu junsen zhang chinese university of hong kong department of economics 2006 pdf+ long term effects of china's great famine in hong kong and mainland china hongbin li douglas almond lena edlund junsen zhang reap working paper 2006 does education pay in urban china estimating returns to education using twins hongbin li pak wai liu ning ma junsen zhang chinese university of hong kong department of economics 2005 pdf+ stanford university all rights reserved 650 723 2300 terms of use copyright complaints rss+ rss xml feeds
